Interface FileEditorManagerListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.EventListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AnnotationsPreloader.AnnotationsPreloaderFileEditorManagerListener, CodeStyleStatusBarWidget, ColumnSelectionModePanel, DvcsStatusWidget, EditorBasedStatusBarPopup, EditorBasedWidget, EncodingPanel, EncodingWidget, FileEditorManagerAdapter, FileTypeUsageCounterCollector.MyFileEditorManagerListener, GitBranchWidget, HgIncomingOutgoingWidget, HgStatusWidget, LightEditPositionWidget, LineSeparatorPanel, NavBarListener, PositionPanel, TestFailedLineManager, TogglePopupHintsPanel

    public interface FileEditorManagerListener
extends java.util.EventListener
    Listener for FileEditorManager events. All methods are invoked in EDT.
